'''康懋达64'''（{{lang-en|Commodore 64}}），也稱為C64、CBM 64或在瑞典被稱作VIC-64<ref>[http://www.lemon64.com/museum/view.php?id=274&genre=manualcom VIC 64 Användarmanual] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lemon64.com/museum/view.php?id=274&genre=manualcom |date=20180922010733 }}. Image of Swedish edition of the VIC 64 user's manual. Retrieved on March 12, 2007.</ref>是由[[康懋達國際|康懋達國際]]於1982年1月推出的[[8位元|8位元]][[家用電腦|家用電腦]]（首次在1982年1月7日至10日，於拉斯維加斯消費電子展上展出。）<ref>Info World, 1 Feb. 1982,[https://books.google.com/books?id=dT4EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA1&dq=%22consumer+electronics+show%22+1982+commodore&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiN-IiOm4XTAhWDyyYKHc7zAM0Q6AEIHDAA#v=onepage&q=%22consumer%20electronics%20show%22%201982%20commodore&f=false].</ref>。
它在[[金氏世界紀錄大全|金氏世界紀錄]]中被列為所有時間最暢銷的單一電腦型號，<ref name="cnn.com">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/TECH/gaming.gadgets/05/09/commodore.64.reborn/|title=The Commodore 64, that '80s computer icon, lives again|publisher=|accessdate=November 17, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224073113/http://www.cnn.com/2011/TECH/gaming.gadgets/05/09/commodore.64.reborn/}}</ref> 獨立估計出售數量在1000至1700萬台之間。<ref name="PageTable"/>批量生產始於1982年初，在同年8月以{{US$|595|1982}}價格販售。<ref name="ieee85">{{cite journal|last2=Wallich |first2=Paul |date=March 1985 |editor-last= |editor-first= |editor-link= |title=Design case history: the Commodore 64 |url=https://spectrum.ieee.org/ns/pdfs/commodore64_mar1985.pdf |journal=IEEE Spectrum |series= |language= |location= |publisher= |volume= |issue= |pages=48–58 |arxiv= |bibcode= |doi= |isbn= |issn=0018-9235 |oclc= |pmc= |pmid= |id= |quote= |postscript= |ref= |separator= |last1=Perry |first1=Tekla S. |authorlink1= |authorlink2= |trans_title= |accessdate=2011-11-12 |laysource= |laysummary= |laydate= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513181613/http://spectrum.ieee.org/ns/pdfs/commodore64_mar1985.pdf |archivedate=2012-05-13 |df= }}</ref><ref name="mayhem64_co_uk-c64design">{{cite web |title=IEEE Spectrum |url=http://www.mayhem64.co.uk/c64design.htm |date=March 1985 |accessdate=November 3, 2014 |archive-date=2018-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181223115358/http://www.mayhem64.co.uk/c64design.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

其前代機種為{{link-en|VIC-20|Commodore VIC-20}}和{{link-en|Commodore PET}}，C64以其64[[千位元組|KB]]（65,536[[位元組|位元組]]）的[[電腦記憶體|記憶體]]命名。與其他早期系統（如[[Apple_II|Apple II]]和Atari 800）相比，它具有卓越的聲音和圖形規格，具有多色[[精靈_(電腦圖形學)|精靈]]和更進階的聲音處理器。

1980年代大部分時間，C64主導著低端電腦市場。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/152528/comm64.html|title=Inside the Commodore 64|date=November 4, 2008|work=PCWorld|accessdate=November 17, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320172847/https://www.pcworld.com/article/152528/comm64.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在一段相當長的一段時期（1983年－1986年），C64在美國市場份額為30%至40%，每年銷售量為200萬台，<ref name="Reimer">{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/features/2005/12/total-share/|title=Total share: 30 years of personal computer market share figures|last=Reimer|first=Jeremy|publisher=Ars Technica|accessdate=October 10, 2014|archive-date=2018-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309002124/https://arstechnica.com/features/2005/12/total-share/|dead-url=no}}</ref>遠超過[[IBM_PC相容機|IBM PC相容機]]、[[蘋果公司|蘋果]]電腦和[[雅達利|雅達利]]8位元家庭電腦。後來的雅達利總裁：康懋達創始人之子薩姆·特拉米爾（Sam Tramiel）在一次1989年的採訪中說：“當我在康懋達時，我們連續好幾年，每個月製造40萬台C64。”<ref name="Start 1989">{{cite magazine|last=Naman|first=Mard|title=From Atari's Oval Office An Exclusive Interview With Atari President Sam Tramiel|magazine=STart|volume=4|issue=2|page=16|publisher=Antic Publishing|location=San Francisco|date=September 1989|url=http://www.atarimagazines.com/startv4n2/ovaloffice.html|issn=|access-date=2017-10-06|archive-date=2019-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107132040/https://www.atarimagazines.com/startv4n2/ovaloffice.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在英國市場，C64雖面臨來自[[BBC_Micro|BBC Micro]]和[[Sinclair_ZX_Spectrum|ZX Spectrum]]的競爭<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-19055707 |title=Commodore 64 turns 30: What do today's kids make of it? |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |accessdate=2017-03-18 |archive-date=2021-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320172910/https://www.bbc.com/news/av/technology-19055707 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但C64仍然是英國最受歡迎的兩台電腦之一。<ref name="Billboard Nov 1962">{{cite magazine | last = Zuckerman | first = Faye | title = Now Playing | magazine =BillBoard | volume = 96 | issue = 46 | page =23 | publisher = Billboard Publications | date = 17 Nov 1984  | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=JCQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA23 | issn = 0006-2510  | accessdate = June 8, 2015}}</ref>

Commodore 64的一部分成功在於其於在正規零售商店銷售，而不僅只限於電子產品或電腦愛好者專賣店。 Commodore在內部生產了許多部件來控制成本，包括來自[[MOS科技|MOS Technology]]的定制[[積體電路|積體電路]]。
將其與[[福特T型車|福特T型車]]相比較，同樣是透過創造力和負擔得起的大規模生產，來達到向中產階級家庭帶來新技術的作用。<ref name="Kahney">{{cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/culture/lifestyle/news/2003/09/60349 |title=Grandiose Price for a Modest PC |last=Kahney |first=Leander |date=September 9, 2003 |publisher=CondéNet, Inc |accessdate=September 13, 2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080914001847/http://www.wired.com/culture/lifestyle/news/2003/09/60349 |archivedate=September 14, 2008 |df= }}</ref> Commodore 64已經開發了大約10,000個商業軟體，包括開發工具，辦公生產力應用和[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]。<ref name="Impact">{{cite web|url=http://www.computerhistory.org/events/video/75/|title=Impact of the Commodore 64: A 25th Anniversary Celebration|publisher=Computer History Museum|accessdate=September 13, 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003111509/http://www.computerhistory.org/events/video/75/|archive-date=2017-10-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 而C64[[模擬器|模擬器]]的出現，使得人們能夠在現代電腦或兼容的[[電子遊樂器|電子遊樂器]]上，運行這些C64程式。 C64也被稱為普及電腦，今天仍被電腦愛好者使用。<ref name="use">{{cite web|last=Swenson|first=Reid C.|title=What is a Commodore Computer? A Look at the Incredible History and Legacy of the Commodore Home Computers|publisher=OldSoftware.Com|year=2007|url=http://www.oldsoftware.com/history.html|accessdate=November 19, 2007|archive-date=2018-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180402193935/http://www.oldsoftware.com/history.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 此外2014年一項研究表明，在2011年（即停產17年後），Commodore 64的品牌認知度仍有87%。<ref name="cnn.com" />

